snippet: Two U.N. peacekeepers were killed and nine others injured in a suicide attack on a patrol base in northern Mali, the U.N. peacekeeping mission (MINUSMA) said on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Suicide Bomber Attacks U.N. Base in Northern Mali, Kills Two
headline.main: Suicide Bomber Attacks U.N. Base in Northern Mali, Kills Two

lead_paragraph: Two U.N. peacekeepers were killed and nine others injured in a suicide attack on a patrol base in northern Mali, the U.N. peacekeeping mission (MINUSMA) said on Saturday.
